Usage: partitionPushSpecialWires [-help] [-checkOnly] [-keepNetName] {-nets <list_of_net_names> | -overlappingPartitions <string>}

-help                               # Prints out the command usage
-checkOnly                          # Checks if selected nets spcial-routes are
                                    # in syn or not (bool, optional)
-keepNetName                        # Preserve the net-name in partitions
                                    # (bool, optional)
-nets <list_of_net_names>           # To specify list of nets to consider
                                    # (string, optional)
-overlappingPartitions <string>     # for special nets overlapping the
                                    # partition (string, optional)